.RE
.PP
\fI1\fR
.RS 4
permission denied
.RE
.PP
\fI2\fR
.RS 4
invalid combination of options
.RE
.PP
\fI3\fR
.RS 4
unexpected failure, nothing done
.RE
.PP
\fI4\fR
.RS 4
unexpected failure,
passwd
file missing
.RE
.PP
\fI5\fR
.RS 4
passwd
file busy, try again
.RE
.PP
\fI6\fR
.RS 4
invalid argument to option
.RE
